      About this item

      • 【Voice/BT Remote Controller】 Lumary smart recessed lighting 6 inch work with Alexa and Google Assistant or Remote Controller (sold separately, please search Lumary BT Remote Controller). A simple dialogue/button turns your Lumary LED recessed lights on or off, changes colors and adjusts brightness. Multiple control options for easy daily use.
      • 【High Quality & Easy Installation】Lumary canless LED recessed light is very easy to install. Cut a hole in the ceiling with a 160MM hole template, connect the Jbox to the cable, and use a spring clip to fix it on the ceiling. Ultra-thin body is suitable for outdoor retrofit and new decoration. If you have a very small ceiling space, this light will be your first choice.
      • 【 2700-6500k Adjustable & Brightness】 Lumary 6 inch smart WiFi recessed lights support 1%-100% brightness adjustment, providing warm and cool white from 2700K to 6500K to meet your different lighting needs. (Note: Not compatible with any dimmer switch, it will affect the service life.)
      • 【RGB Adjustable & Music Sync】 Lumary smart WiFi recessed lights provide 16 million colors and 8 scene modes to create the perfect lighting atmosphere. You can DIY the scene mode you want. The recessed light can also change color with the beat of the music or the sound of the game. This feature is only available for APP, with no built-in microphone or speaker.
      • 【Lumary APP Control】Download Lumary App, You just lay on the sofa and you can easily control all of the Lumary black recessed lights 6inch functions through the app, enjoying the convenience and fun of smart lighting. Note: only support 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi.
      • 【Group control】You may control the black smart recessed lighting in several rooms at the same time, such as the living room, kitchen, bedroom, soffit, etc. Save you more time!
      • 【Schedule & Remote Control】You can set this mode to turn on or off the canless Wafer Downlight according to your wake-up and sleep time. When you turn on this mode, you don't have to turn the lights on and off manually. You control your lamps remotely anytime, anywhere through the app.
      • 【Share the device & Memory Function】You can share the device with your family, and family members can all control the black recessed canless lighting together and enjoy the smart fun. With memory, the function will stay at the last setting you choose while turned on again, no need to reset it.
      • 【APP Connection Use】 ①Download the APP named Lumary and enjoy intelligent control.②Repeat turning the smart wifi LED recessed lights switch on and off 3 times to make the light flash into the paired WiFi mode.③Tap on Add Devices on the home page and the hub will auto-connection. NOTE: Only support 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi.④With memory function will stay at the last setting you choose while turning it on again, no need to reset it.
      • 【After-sales service】Lumary has a professional after-sales team, if you encounter any problems in the follow-up use, please feel free to contact us will provide you with technical support in a timely manner.

                  How customer reviews and ratings work

                  Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

                  To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

                  5 out of 5 stars
                  Excellent quality
                  I recently purchased the Lumary Smart Recessed Light 6-Inch Canless LED Downlight, and I am extremely impressed with its quality and functionality. This smart light has quickly become a favorite of my husband, and for good reason. The Lumary Smart Recessed Light is compatible with Wi-Fi and Bluetooth, allowing for seamless integration with various smart home systems, including Alexa and Google Assistant. This feature offers convenient control options, as my husband can now effortlessly adjust the lighting using voice commands or smartphone applications. The quality of this canless LED downlight is excellent. It provides a bright and uniform illumination of 1100 lumens, ensuring sufficient lighting in my living room. The 6-inch size of the light fits perfectly into our ceiling, giving a clean and sleek look without the need for a traditional recessed can. The included junction box makes installation easy and hassle-free. One of the things I appreciate most about this smart recessed light is its color-changing ability. With the RGB feature, my husband can customize the lighting to suit any mood or occasion. Whether he wants a warm and cozy ambiance or a vibrant and colorful setting, this light offers endless possibilities. The effectiveness of this Lumary Smart Recessed Light is truly commendable. It has significantly enhanced the lighting in our home, providing a pleasant and well-lit environment. The ability to control the light remotely has also added convenience and flexibility to our daily routines.Overall, I am highly satisfied with the Lumary Smart Recessed Light 6-Inch Canless LED Downlight. Its excellent quality, smart capabilities, and customizable lighting options have made it a valuable addition to our home. I highly recommend considering this product.

                    I like these LED smart recessed lights because the lights came with a junction box, making it easy to connect them to my existing electrical system. Additionally, the canless design eliminates the need for bulky recessed cans, which gives my entire room a cool and modern look.

                    Furthermore, these lights can change colors, I just had to download the Lumary app on my iPhone and pair these lights via Bluetooth and Wi-Fi, then I am able to customize these lights anytime according to my mood or just to set the vibe in different occasions.

                    Whether I want a warm and cozy ambiance or a vibrant and colorful atmosphere in my room, these smart lights can even change colors according to the music or change colors if I am watching a movie or game, with the vibrations they keep changing colors.

                    Additionally, these lights are compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant, and I can simply use my voice to control these lights and adjust their brightness, change their colors, or turn the lights on/off. I found it super cool and very convenient since these lights added a whole new level of smart functionality to my home.

                    In terms of performance, I personally think these lights are outstanding. With a power output of 13W and a brightness level of 1100 lumens, these lights can go from white to purple, then I can change them to blue or green, and increase or decrease the tone of green, pink, purple, blue and make my entire room glow.

                    And since they are LED lights, I do not regret buying them and I personally believe they will last a long time. Therefore, I am very satisfied with these smart LED recessed lights because they are easy to use and make my room look vibrant and colorful.

With the RGB feature, my husband can customize the lighting to suit any mood or occasion. Whether he wants a warm and cozy ambiance or a vibrant and colorful setting, this light offers endless possibilities. The effectiveness of this Lumary Smart Recessed Light is truly commendable. It has significantly enhanced the lighting in our home, providing a pleasant and well-lit environment. The ability to control the light remotely has also added convenience and flexibility to our daily routines.
                    Overall, I am highly satisfied with the Lumary Smart Recessed Light 6-Inch Canless LED Downlight. Its excellent quality, smart capabilities, and customizable lighting options have made it a valuable addition to our home. I highly recommend considering this product.
